---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About  Amaljith Kuttamath" description="AI Engineer at Sorcero, building retrieval pipelines and knowledge graphs for healthcare.">
  <div class="about-content animate-in">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm an AI Engineer at <a href="https://sorcero.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sorcero</a>, based in Arlington, VA. I build the systems that help healthcare professionals make better decisions  retrieval pipelines that surface relevant medical literature, knowledge graphs that connect drugs, diseases, and clinical trials, and NLP tools that extract meaning from messy, real-world data.
    </p>

    <p>
      Before Sorcero, I was a Senior NLP Research Fellow at George Mason's TraCCC, where I worked on applying language models to security research. Before that, I built enterprise data pipelines at INECTA, designed predictive maintenance systems at RadianArc, and wrote software at TCS. I got my start interning at ISRO, which is where I first realized I wanted to work on hard technical problems.
    </p>

    <p>
      I have an MS in Data Analytics from George Mason University and a BTech in Electrical Engineering from GITAM.
    </p>

    <h2>Tools I Use</h2>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h3>AI / ML</h3>
        <p>PyTorch, Transformers, LangChain, LlamaIndex, spaCy, sentence-transformers</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h3>Data</h3>
        <p>Neo4j, Elasticsearch, PostgreSQL, Databricks, Spark</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h3>Cloud</h3>
        <p>Google Cloud (Vertex AI), Azure (Data Factory, Data Lake), AWS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h3>Languages</h3>
        <p>Python, SQL, JavaScript, TypeScript</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Timeline</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">AI Engineer</span>
          <span class="timeline-company">Sorcero</span>
        </div>
        <p class="timeline-desc">RAG pipelines, knowledge graphs, and NLP for healthcare</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">Senior NLP Research Fellow</span>
          <span class="timeline-company">George Mason TraCCC</span>
        </div>
        <p class="timeline-desc">Language models applied to security research</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">Data Engineer</span>
          <span class="timeline-company">INECTA</span>
        </div>
        <p class="timeline-desc">50+ EDI pipelines on Azure and Databricks</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">Data Scientist</span>
          <span class="timeline-company">RadianArc</span>
        </div>
        <p class="timeline-desc">Predictive maintenance from industrial sensor data</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">Software Engineer</span>
          <span class="timeline-company">TCS</span>
        </div>
        <p class="timeline-desc">Enterprise software development</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div>
          <span class="timeline-role">Intern</span>
